Resurrection. Ad [Addendum] date, cf. Suiocide of Saul, 1562. The forms of the figures, the rock formation, particularly the 2 soldiers on the right, cf. the soldiers approaching Saul from the dark pl. 47 centre. The soldier on the left foreground seen from the back, cf. (pl. 31), cf. Witt 'Templar' in Dulle Griet (pl. 38).
